These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
4 different pets are kept: mouse, rat, goldfish, dog
House: art-deco, craftsman, palace, modern
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, soy-milk, lemonade
1. the craftsman house is the owner of the dog##1
2. the palace house is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the craftsman house is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the art-deco house##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Pet   | rat    | dog    | mouse      | goldfish    |
| House   | modern | craftsman | palace | art-deco |
| Beverage     | lemonade  | almond-milk       | cola    | soy-milk     |

