.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, june, april, july
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, apple, watermelon, papaya
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, montecristo, bongani, vegafina
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person eating papaya is between the owner of the frog and the baccarat-smoker##2
6. the vegafina-smoker is between the person eating papaya and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person eating apple is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
9. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | july | june    | april  | may    |
| Food   | cranberry      | apple  | papaya  | watermelon |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Cigar         | montecristo    | vegafina | bongani | baccarat |

