.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, baseball, soccer
4 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, goat, snake
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, january, march
1. the owner of the goat is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is soccer##2
9. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person eating lemon and the owner of the goldfish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Sport       | lacrosse   | skateboarding   | baseball | soccer |
| Pet         | dog   | goat | snake       | goldfish    |
| Birthday   | january    | february | september  | march    |

