.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, bellflower, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, blues, hip-hop, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, roller, snowmobile, bike
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsrose##1
 3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of blues##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the fan of classical and the person who growsaconite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Flower           | rose  | aconite | balloon-flower     | bellflower |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Music-Genre           | blues       | rock    | hip-hop      | classical           |
| Transport         | skateboard | roller   | bike   | snowmobile         |

