.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, cat, ferret
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, siglo, old-henry, cain
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the cat is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the owner of the rat is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the cain-smoker and the person drinking cola##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Pet           | cat | ferret | chinchilla    | rat     |
| Beverage   | cola      | mirinda       | sprite    | almond-milk       |
| Cigar         | tiparillo     | old-henry       | cain | siglo |

