.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, milk, soy-milk
House: modern, victorian, tower, art-deco
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, white, chestnut, red
1. the modern house is between the person who likes red and the tower house##2
2. the person drinking sprite is between the modern house and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person who likes white and the dutch##2
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the tower house is on the far right##1
9. the victorian house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage           | milk | sprite | tea  | soy-milk |
| House   | victorian      | art-deco       | modern     | tower      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Color         | chestnut   | red    | apricot | white   |

