.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, october, september
City: boston, new-york, miami, rome
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, volleyball, cricket
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is the dutch##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is between the dutch and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 4. the person traveling to miami is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the argentine is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the dutch is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday   | october | december | april  | september  |
| City   | boston       | miami   | new-york | rome    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| Sport     | swimming    | cricket   | rugby    | volleyball  |

