3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the musician is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the dancer is between the paramedic and the modern house##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the gothic-revival house##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
