The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, january, december, november
 1. the american is the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the italian is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person watching crime movies is the person who's birthday is in january##1
