 5. the fan of metal is the british##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person who's birthday is in july##2
10. the italian is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Nationality          | italian        | turkish    | british | american   |
| Movie-Genre           | fantasy | martial-arts | musical   | crime |
